dc_description_s: This line data layer represents trails for LaCrosse County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase LaCrosse_Trails_YE2016.gdb.[A trail or path used for walking, cycling, hiking or other form of non-vehicular transportation. In some cases, other forms of motorized transportation may be permitted on a regular or seasonal basis.]
